Package layers

This package will be used to contain the input layers, calculation layers, and output layers for the Neural Network.
  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    Layer<T>
    This interface will be the individual computational layers for the Neural Network.
    OutputLayer<T,​O>
    This interface will be the final layer or the output layer for the Neural Network.
  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    HiddenLayer
    This class is the hidden layer for the Neural Network.
    HighestOutputLayer
    This class is the output layer for a neural network where the index of the highest value is returned.
    InputLayer
    This is a base input layer and simply outputs the input values received.
    Node
    This class is the node generated for the layers within the neural network.
    RoundedOutputLayer
    This class is the output layer for a Neural Network where it returns the output rounded to the nearest integer.
